      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：允升，大吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject advancing upwards with the welcome (of those above him). There will be great good fortune.</seg>
